t: "Know that whatever spoils you take, one-fifth is for Allah and the Messenger, his close relatives, orphans, the poor, and Ë¹needyËº travellers, if you Ë¹trulyËº believe in Allah and what We revealed to Our servant on that decisive day when the two armies met Ë¹at BadrËº. And Allah is Most Capable of everything"